  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The Crazy Reindeer Hotel is a popular choice</span><span>, having friendly service and a great range of rooms available. The hotel is in a quiet wooded location, around 400 metres from the ski lifts and <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a> village centre, providing beautiful walks through this winter wonderland.</span></p>
<h2><span>Cosy lounge and relaxation</span></h2>
<p>After a day of exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, warm up in front of one of the log fires in the cosy and welcoming public lounge, or relax in the popular bar area with a drink. Alternatively. rejuvenate in the wellness area which features a sauna, steam room, jacuzzi and cold water plunge pool. For the ultimate treat, book a massage or beauty treatment locally, or unwind in the salt room or infrared sauna, which is available for a local fee. There is also an onsite gym so you can prepare for you next Arctic adventure. </p>
<h2>Warm and welcoming rooms </h2>
<p><span>All of the rooms at the Crazy Reindeer are tastefully decorated in a simplistic Nordic style, choose from a cosy room with a sauna or a family duplex which can sleep up to eight. Guest rooms are located in three adjacent buildings which are just a short walk away from the main building. Each of the rooms have all the amenities needed for a relaxing break in Levi, including Wi-Fi, drying closet - some rooms have a sauna and balcony.</span></p>]]></description>
